FBIS4-42664 "drweu109_p_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 GREECE Government Again Blocks EU Aid to Albania Government Again Blocks EU Aid to Albania NC0606190294 Athens ET-1 Television Network in Greek 1800 GMT 6 Jun 94 NC0606190294 Athens ET-1 Television Network Greek BFN [Excerpt] For the second time, Greece has blocked European Union [EU] aid to Albania. National Economy Minister Ioannis Papandoniou refused to give a positive vote to the demand for economic support worth ECU 35 million, which the EU Commission again brought to ECOFIN [EU Council of Finance Ministers]. In Athens, the Foreign Ministry spokesman repeated that Albania's relations with the EU depend on respect for human rights. [passage omitted]
